<includeonly>{{#ifexpr: {{#ask: [[{{PAGENAME:{{{prop|}}}}}::{{FULLPAGENAME}}]] | format=count }} > 0 |{{!}}-
! {{{label|{{PAGENAME:{{{prop|}}}}}}}}
{{!}} {{#ask: [[{{PAGENAME:{{{prop|}}}}}::{{FULLPAGENAME}}]] | format=list }}|}}</includeonly><noinclude>
Renders one backlink row — all pages that point to the current page
via a given property:

 |-
 ! label
 | Page1, Page2, Page3

Skipped when no pages link via that property. Composable with
Category/property-row in custom display tables:

 {| class="wikitable"
 {{Category/property-row | label=Author | value={{Property/Page | value={{{has_author|}}} }} }}
 {{Category/backlink-row | prop=Has author | label=Authored }}
 |}

Costs two `#ask` queries per call — one count check + one list. Used
internally by Category/render-reverse; call directly when you want a
single backlink section without the aggregate "Backlinks" header row.

Parameters:
* prop  - Property page reference (namespaced or bare, e.g. `Has author`).
* label - Optional display label. Defaults to the property's page name.
</noinclude>
